    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Global biogeographic distribution of family Potamolepidae with inserts showing the distribution of Cherokeesia n. gen. within Tennessee and location of Tennessee within the United States. Approximate location of Tennessee is indicated by asterix. Fossils are indicated by plus symbol." ;
