    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288553>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cherokeesia armata n. sp. a, gemmuloscleres type I as large acanthoxeas from notably spiny to almost smooth; b, megascleres of the skeleton as stout acanthoxeas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288553/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

